'''Elon Musk''' is an [[Internet]] and space launch entrepreneur. The first company he co-founded was [[Zip2 Corporation]] in [[1995]], which was later sold to [[Compaq]]'s [[AltaVista]] division. He also co-founded [[PayPal]], which was acquired by [[eBay]] in [[October 2002]].

In [[June 2002]] he founded his third company, [[SpaceX]], which he is currently the [[CEO]] and [[Chief Technology Officer]] of. This company is developing space [[launch vehicle]]s, with an emphasis on low cost and high reliability. The first two launch vehicles planned are the [[Falcon I]] and [[Falcon V]] rockets.

